{"arkId":"cl010097267","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010097267","modified ":"2025-09-17","title":"Bo\u00eetier de forme \u0022tambour\u0022","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Bo\u00eetier de forme \u0022tambour\u0022"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Fran\u00e7ois II (1559-1560) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Valois-Angoul\u00eame) ; Charles IX (1560-1574) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Valois-Angoul\u00eame)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1550 - 1575","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1550,"endYear":1575,"imprecision":"","text":"3e quart du XVIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Gruber, Hans","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1530","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1597","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 686","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Bo\u00eetier de forme tambour, aplati pr\u00e9sentant un d\u00e9cor moul\u00e9, cisel\u00e9 et partiellement ajour\u00e9. Couvercle orn\u00e9 d\u0027un m\u00e9daillon en bas-relief encadr\u00e9 de rinceaux ajour\u00e9s et de t\u00eates d\u0027angelot, repr\u00e9sentant le Christ crucifi\u00e9, la Vierge et saint Jean. Sur le fond, apparait en bas-relief saint Georges terrassant le dragon dans un encadrement de cuirs ajour\u00e9s et de moulures concentriques. Carrure d\u00e9cor\u00e9e d\u0027une frise ajour\u00e9e de rubans crois\u00e9s. Cadran \u00e0 double tour d\u0027heures ; chiffres I \u00e0 XII et 13 \u00e0 24 grav\u00e9s en relief ; au centre, ouverture o\u00f9 se logeait le cercle horaire du r\u00e9veil. Timbe encore fix\u00e9 \u00e0 la bo\u00eete.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; monogramme HG et deux pelles crois\u00e9es","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"2,5","displayDimension":"2,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"6,6","displayDimension":"6,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Nuremberg = N\u00fcremberg (Allemagne-\u003EBavi\u00e8re)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"collection Alexandre-Charles Sauvageot (1781-1860) ; donation en 1856.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Sauvageot, Alexandre-Charles","note":"","role":", Collectionneur ; Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"donation","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de donation","value":"1856","startYear":1856,"endYear":1856}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"donation"}],"period":[{"value":"Fran\u00e7ois II (1559-1560)"},{"value":"Charles IX (1560-1574)"}],"place":[{"value":"Nuremberg = N\u00fcremberg"}],"objectType":[{"value":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliographyDate":"2000","bibliographyDetail":"p. 59, n\u00b0 24","comparison":false},{"bib